{
  "stem": "10283.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Blachmann and her daughter will come back again, I can let them go to see you once [? and ?] [? anything. ?] So a very strange situation started.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They opened the jail doors, and we walked in town alone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to this lady.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she was a very gracious lady.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She made a beautiful tea for us with patisserie and with everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were human beings all of a sudden, again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when this was done, we marched back to jail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed in jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it was really strange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then winter started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said, do you have anything to wear?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't have any.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we say, come to the store and pick out whatever you like, you know, what you need, underwear and stockings.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Swiss winters are pretty severe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then we had a little bit of money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in the-- like in the thrift shop, we bought some ski boots from her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and so we had clothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then after that, we were a few weeks with the Salvation Army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because somehow, our papers didn't come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in the Salvation Army in the home and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They tried to convert us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise they were very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was even sick there, and they called the doctor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they treated me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the meantime, I guess my mother had communication with this Mrs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Morton's ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she had come the same route that we came with her two children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She made it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
